html
  head
    title Game Rules
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/css/style.css")

  body

    header
      h1 Loop Quest

    main

      .container

        .rules-box

          h2 Game Rules

          p Read the instructions before starting the game.

          h3 How to Play

          ul
            li Roll the dice.
            li Move your token on the game board.
            li If you land on a QR tile, scan the QR code.
            li Answer the Python loop question.
            li If your answer is wrong, skip your next turn.
            li If your answer is correct, continue playing.

          h3 Scoring

          p
            | Final score is calculated based on:
          
          p
            | Correct Answers / Total Attempts × 100%

          h3 Winning Condition

          p
            | The player with the highest score wins.

          p.return-message
            | Return to the physical board to begin the game.